(51, 2, 'How much water should I drink for a day.', 'Drink at least 8 cups (64 oz) of water each day and monitor your urine output.', '2026-04-24 00:45:59', '2026-04-24 00:45:59'),
(52, 2, 'Can you tell me the meal plan for today.', 'No data found in the database for a meal plan.', '2026-04-24 03:10:46', '2026-04-24 03:10:46'),
(53, 2, 'Can you tell me the meal plan for today.', 'I\'m sorry, I don’t have that information in my database.\n\nHowever, I can suggest a general meal plan based on my knowledge:\n\nFor a balanced diet, consider eating at least three main meals with some snacks in between.\n\nHere is a sample meal plan:\n\nBreakfast:\n- No data found in the database for breakfast.\n\nLunch:\n- No data found in the database for lunch.\n\nDinner:\n- No data found in the database for dinner.\n\nTotal Calories:\n- No data found in the database to calculate total calories.', '2026-04-24 03:11:28', '2026-04-24 03:11:28'),
