(58, 2, 'Can you tell me the meal plan for today.', 'Breakfast:\n- Grilled Chicken Breast (300 calories)\n- Oatmeal with Banana (250 calories)\n\nLunch:\n- Grilled Salmon (400 calories)\n- Mixed Greens Salad (150 calories)\n\nDinner:\n- Grilled Turkey Breast (350 calories)\n- Steamed Broccoli (55 calories)\n\nTotal Calories:\n- 1305 calories', '2026-04-24 03:38:42', '2026-04-24 03:38:42'),
