(65, 2, 'Yesterday, I do plank exercise but my belly feel pain a lot. What should I do to reduce pain.', 'Stop the plank exercise immediately. Rest your belly for a few days. Gently stretch your stomach muscles. If the pain is severe or persists, consider consulting a doctor to rule out any underlying issues.', '2026-04-24 03:48:11', '2026-04-24 03:48:11'),
(66, 2, 'Yesterday, I do plank exercise but my belly feel pain a lot. What should I do to reduce pain.', 'Stop the plank exercise immediately. Rest your belly for a few days. Gently stretch your stomach muscles. If the pain is severe or persists, consider consulting a doctor to rule out any underlying issues.', '2026-04-24 03:49:21', '2026-04-24 03:49:21'),
